            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2477e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  For each contract assigned for administration, the contract administration office (CAO) (see <xref href="FAR-i1125359.dita#i1125359"
                        base="i1125359"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">2.101</xref>) shall-</p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d2466e26">
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2477e30" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
